    %% RBAC Flow
    OperatorSA -->|bound via| OperatorCRB
    OperatorCRB -->|grants| OperatorCR
    OperatorCR -->|create, manage| LMEvalJobCRD
    OperatorCR -->|create, manage| K8sJob
    OperatorCR -->|read| ConfigMap
    OperatorCR -->|read| Secret

    %% Operator creates Job
    OperatorSA -->|creates| JobPod

    %% Job security context
    JobPod --- NonRoot
    JobPod --- BaseImage
    JobPod --- WritableDirs
    JobPod --- NoPorts

    %% Secret usage
    JobPod -.->|uses| HFToken
    OperatorSA -.->|"uses (build time)"| GitAuth

